You don't get it, Priyanka is
my..

1602
01:52:13,000 --> 01:52:14,333
Priyanka is my?

1603
01:52:14,333 --> 01:52:16,583
I don't want to hear another
word!

1604
01:52:16,583 --> 01:52:20,750
Guys like you always take
girls like us for a ride!

1605
01:52:20,750 --> 01:52:22,917
Was it wrong that I love you?

1606
01:52:22,917 --> 01:52:26,458
Are you done? I love you too!

1607
01:52:27,500 --> 01:52:28,792
Can I say something?

1608
01:52:30,667 --> 01:52:32,208
Priyanka is my cousin.

1609
01:52:34,250 --> 01:52:37,292
That's right. He's told
me so much about you.

1610
01:52:37,292 --> 01:52:41,042
It's not good to doubt like
that.
Kunal, I'll leave now.

1611
01:52:43,375 --> 01:52:46,792
