1713
02:00:21,833 --> 02:00:23,208
Drama queen!

1714
02:00:28,208 --> 02:00:34,208
I feel better. I should leave.

1715
02:00:35,042 --> 02:00:38,333
I guess I'll call you.

1716
02:00:38,625 --> 02:00:40,208
I guess you will.

1717
02:00:43,958 --> 02:00:47,583
Jai, lunch?

1718
02:00:48,083 --> 02:00:52,625
