an important lunch meeting.

1719
02:00:52,625 --> 02:00:56,250
Really? I forgot you
even have to work.

1720
02:00:57,083 --> 02:00:58,583
Something like that.

1721
02:00:58,750 --> 02:01:00,125
Is it interesting?

1722
02:01:00,833 --> 02:01:02,833
Well, it is nice to
see you again, Jai.

1723
02:01:02,833 --> 02:01:04,250
And it's really nice
to extend this contract.

1724
02:01:04,250 --> 02:01:05,917
Thank you, sir.

1725
02:01:06,125 --> 02:01:07,583
