you'll repent it all your life.

1753
02:03:16,500 --> 02:03:20,625
Take care buddy... see you.

1754
02:03:21,125 --> 02:03:23,250
Ma'am... pleasure.

1755
02:03:28,958 --> 02:03:30,583
Thank you... so much!

1756
02:03:30,583 --> 02:03:31,792
It's okay.

1757
